title: How Do Volcanoes Make Smoke Rings?
description:
Order your 2024 SciShow Calendar, the Pin of the Month, and all SciShow merch here: https://dftba.com/scishow

Occasionally, a volcano coughs up a ring of fog. How does it create that whimsical shape, and how similar is it to the smoke rings humans can make?

Hosted by: Stefan Chin
